In the REST call what does the “id” mean? 
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "query",
  "params": {
      "type": 1,
      "chaincodeID":{
          "name": &lt;address&gt;
      },
      "ctorMsg": {
         "function":"query",
         "args":["a"]
      }
  },
  "id": 5   ---&gt; What is id here?
}
